1. *Čuvaj* se od promena vremena. (Take care of the weather changes.)
2. On je vrlo odgovoran i *čuva* svoje obaveze. (He is very responsible and keeps his promises.)
3. Ona je naša čuvarica, pa joj verujemo. (She is our guardian, so we trust her.)
4. Ona *čuva* svoju lojalnost. (She keeps her loyalty.)
5. Ne zaboravi *čuvati* svoje stvari. (Don't forget to keep your things.)